Don't Look Down: Rope Men
Personal cameras and drones follow industrial abseilers as they scale iconic buildings such as Tower Bridge, and Alexandra Palace. There's trouble in Dubai when a specialist team are suspended 800ft up a skyscraper in 118-degree heat, and climbers in Plymouth also face problems when they meet a protective mother seagull defending her nest of chicks.
